---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us — YT Downloader" description="Learn more about YT Downloader, the team behind it, and our mission to provide the best free media downloading experience.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-24 w-full">
    <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:text-body prose-headings:text-ink max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-1.28px] mb-8">About Us</h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">We built YT Downloader because we were tired of the internet being full of slow, ad-ridden, and unsafe video downloaders.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our mission is simple: to provide the fastest, cleanest, and most reliable way to save your favorite media for offline use. In an era where digital content is often ephemeral, we believe users should have a straightforward tool to archive educational videos, independent music, and personal favorites without jumping through hoops or risking their digital security.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Why We're Different</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>User-Centric Design:</strong> No pop-ups, no hidden buttons, no confusing interfaces. Just a clean, minimal design that gets out of your way.</li>
        <li><strong>Speed First:</strong> We utilize an optimized backend architecture to fetch and process your files as quickly as physically possible.</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy Respected:</strong> We don't want your data. We don't ask for logins, and we immediately discard download logs. Your privacy is paramount.</li>
        <li><strong>Completely Free:</strong> Premium features like 4K video and 320kbps audio shouldn't be locked behind a paywall. We offer everything for free.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">The Technology</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">YT Downloader is built using modern web technologies to ensure a snappy, responsive experience on any device. Whether you are on a high-end desktop Mac or a budget Android smartphone, our platform adapts to give you the best experience possible.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
